OL,6,FCouncil tax bills for Band D homes are
OL,7,Fincreasing by #116 on average across
OL,8,Fthe North East, York and North
OL,9,FYorkshire.
OL,11,FMost local councils have again opted
OL,12,Fto increase charges by five percent,
OL,13,Fwhich is the limit without triggering
OL,14,Fa local referendum or getting special
OL,15,Fpermission from the government.
