OL,3,CCouncil tax Band D rising average #116
OL,4,Cin North East - how does yours compare?
OL,6,FOur region has among the highest
OL,7,Fcouncil tax rates in the country,
OL,8,Flinked to many parts of the North East
OL,9,Fhaving a majority of smaller and less
OL,10,Fvaluable properties, meaning councils
OL,11,Fstruggle to raise the money needed to
OL,12,Fdeliver services.
OL,14,FCouncils set charges each year for
OL,15,Fstandard Band D homes.
OL,17,FProperties are grouped into eight
OL,18,Fbands, still based on what they would
OL,19,Fhave been worth in 1991.
