OL,3,CCouncil tax Band D rising average #116
OL,4,Cin North East - how does yours compare?
OL,6,FThe lowest value, Band A, homes are
OL,7,Fcharged two-thirds of the Band D rate,
OL,8,Fwhile the highest value, Band H, homes
OL,9,Fare charged double the Band D rate.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday evening (19 March), the
OL,12,FLabour MP for Hartlepool Jonathan
OL,13,FBrash led a debate in the House of
OL,14,FCommons, calling for an overhaul of
OL,15,Fthe system.
