OL,4,Cin North East - how does yours compare?
OL,6,FHe said: "Someone can live in a multi-
OL,7,Fmillion-pound property in London and
OL,8,Fstill pay less council tax than
OL,9,Fsomeone in a terraced house in
OL,10,FHartlepool. It is not right. It is not
OL,11,Ffair. It must change."
OL,13,FLocal Government Minister Jim McMahon
OL,14,Fresponded: "Although the government
OL,15,Frecognise the arguments in favour of
OL,16,Fcouncil tax revaluation and reform,
OL,17,Fthere are currently no plans to reform
OL,18,Fcouncil tax in this parliament."
